%N A391551 Number of fixed polylozenges with n cells.
%C A391551 A cell of a polylozenge is a lozenge consisting of two adjacent equilateral triangles in the triangular grid.
%C A391551 There are three distinct orientations of a cell relative to a fixed triangular grid, so a(1) = 3.
